OL,3,CPolice hunting driver after elderly
OL,4,Cwoman dies during a trip to shops
OL,6,FPolice are hunting for a driver after
OL,7,Fan elderly woman died following a hit-
OL,8,Fand-run crash during a trip to her
OL,9,Flocal shop in Liverpool.
OL,11,FThe woman, 81, was hit by a car in
OL,12,FLongmoor Lane, Fazakerley, on Friday
OL,13,Fafternoon, Merseyside Police said.
OL,15,FThe pensioner, who lived locally,
OL,16,Fsuffered serious injuries and was
OL,17,Ftaken to Aintree Hospital where she
OL,18,Fdied a short time later, officers said.
