OL,3,CPolice hunting driver after elderly
OL,4,Cwoman dies during a trip to shops
OL,6,FPolice were called to the scene at
OL,7,F4.15pm on Friday and on Saturday
OL,8,Fmorning were continuing to search for
OL,9,Fthe driver and the dark-coloured car,
OL,10,Fwhich did not stop after the incident
OL,11,Fnear to the junction with Third Avenue.
OL,13,FOfficers are appealing to anyone who
OL,14,Fhas CCTV or doorbell footage that
OL,15,Fcaptured the incident to come forward
OL,16,Fand said they are particularly
OL,17,Finterested in talking to any motorists
OL,18,Fwho were in the area who may have
OL,19,Fdashcam footage of the incident.
