OL,3,CPolice hunting driver after elderly
OL,4,Cwoman dies during a trip to shops
OL,6,FLongmoor Lane was cordoned off while
OL,7,Fforensics were carried out. According
OL,8,Fto traffic sensors, the road was
OL,9,Freopened by Saturday morning.
OL,11,FSuperintendent Siobhan Russell, said:
OL,12,F"The 81-year-old victim had only
OL,13,Fpopped out to shops and now her family
OL,14,Fare trying to come to terms with her
OL,15,Floss.
OL,17,F"Specialist officers are providing
OL,18,Fthem with support at this tragic time.
