OL,3,CPolice hunting driver after elderly
OL,4,Cwoman dies during a trip to shops
OL,6,F"At this stage of the investigation
OL,7,Fthe full circumstances of the incident
OL,8,Fare still being established and I
OL,9,Fwould like to take this opportunity
OL,10,Ffor the driver of the car to search
OL,11,Ftheir conscience and come forward.
OL,13,F"I would also like to appeal to anyone
OL,14,Fwho has any information which could
OL,15,Fhelp us identify the driver to come
OL,16,Fforward.
OL,18,F"We also want to find the car, which
OL,19,Fmay have sustained damage as a result
OL,20,Fof the collision and may have been
OL,21,Fparked up or even abandoned."
